headline: Expedia (EXPE): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Expedia has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 9.7% to $212.24 per share while the index has gained 9.7%.
